metadata.title: OpenAI Unveils GPT-5.3-Codex: Revolutionizing Software Development with Autonomous AI
metadata.excerpt: OpenAI has launched GPT-5.3-Codex, its most advanced agentic coding model to date. Featuring a 25% speed increase over its predecessor, the model can autonomously manage the entire software lifecycle, from research to deployment. It notably assisted in its own development, marking a significant milestone in self-improving artificial intelligence capabilities. 📲 OpenAI GPT-5.3-Codex Launched: New AI Agentic Model Can Autonomously Build, Debug and Manage Software.
